# Environment Configuration for Content Decoder Batch Analyze

# =============================================================================
# Anthropic API (OPTIONAL - Only needed for --mode=api)
# =============================================================================
# If you're using Claude Code CLI, you DON'T need this!
# Only uncomment if you want to use API mode (--mode=api) for automation
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Airtable API (Required for Airtable save target)
# =============================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://airtable.com/account (Personal Access Token)
# Get your Base ID from the URL when viewing your base
# Example URL: https://airtable.com/appXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/tblYYYYYYYYYYYYYY/viwZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ
#              Base ID is: ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
AIRTABLE_API_KEY=patXXXXXXXXXXXXXX.xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
AIRTABLE_BASE_ID=appXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

# Alternative token name (airtable-saver.js checks both)
# AIRTABLE_TOKEN=patXXXXXXXXXXXXXX.xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# =============================================================================
# Notion API (Required for Notion save target - legacy)
# =============================================================================
# Get your integration token from: https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
# NOTION_API_KEY=secret_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
# NOTION_DATABASE_ID=XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

# =============================================================================
# Optional Configuration
# =============================================================================
# LLM Model (default: claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929)
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929

# Temperature for analysis (default: 0.3)
# ANTHROPIC_TEMPERATURE=0.3

# Max tokens for API responses (default: 8000)
# ANTHROPIC_MAX_TOKENS=8000

# =============================================================================
# Setup Instructions
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Fill in your API keys (remove the example values)
#
# 3. For Airtable setup:
#    - Create a base using AIRTABLE-SCHEMA.md
#    - Generate a Personal Access Token with data.records:read and data.records:write scopes
#    - Copy your Base ID from the Airtable URL
#
# 4. Never commit .env to git (it's already in .gitignore)
